Changes for Perl extension Test-POE-Stopping

1.06 Mon 13 Sep 2010
	- Support ref-count changes in POE 1.291
	- Temporarily remove the version lock on POE::API::Peek

1.05 Thu  8 Oct 2009
	- Adding differentiated queue tracking (from vs to vs total)
	- Adding a copy of the ref refcount to the diagnostics
	- Adding detection of attempted shutdown within a nested ->call

1.04 Fri 11 Sep 2009
	- Adding diagnostics on the state of the various sessions
	- Updated to Module::Install 0.91

0.03 Wed 11 Mar 2009
	- No functional changes
	- Updated Perl dependency to 5.6
	- Updated to Module::Install 0.79

0.02 Sun 12 Jul 2008
	- No functional changes
	- Added the missing Changes file
	- Updated to Module::Install 0.75
